The key challenge here is avoiding a Legend State cascade: updating `lastSavedAt` inside the save handler triggers the store subscription, which schedules another save. We solve this with a module-level flag checked before the debounce timer reset — synchronous Legend State notifications ensure the flag is visible when the subscriber fires.
